person.persName: William Bryant Fishback (Jefferson County, Kentucky, farmer.)

body.p: Jefferson County, Kentucky, farmer. Virginia, native. Son of Michael Fishback and Serilda Wagoner Fishback. Farmer in Jefferson County, Kentucky, in 1860.
